{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I got involved in the Agadir earthquake.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the ambassador in Rome, the Moroccan ambassador, phoned me to say that they'd had this terrible earthquake.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew a general in the Air Force who had helped us when we were filming, so I woke him up and asked him if he could lend us a plane.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine some-- how stupid can you be?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had a friend who was with [? squibs, ?] you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got a lot of medicine for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a little bit of time to wait.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The general said he was going to send a plane.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went in a hospital nearby, and when I left about an hour later, there's seven young doctors, students, came with me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we wait at the airport, and we wait, and we wait, and just about dawn, a little dot appears.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody's furious at me because they think here we are here with all this equipment and these doctors, and no plane.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A little dot appears, and then a few minutes later the big plane--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Agadir.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were one of the first planes to land there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I became quite close friends with the crown prince, who is now the king there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he's the most incredible man there ever was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He worked over 20 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how he did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was the-- I suppose is the person that I-- I would say I admire the most of anyone I know today.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And another one is-- I've been involved with the Afghan thing a lot, too-- is Yaqub Khan, the foreign minister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And President Zia, I got to be very good friends with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
